        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> (1 comment)\n\nin try-with-resource block, both response and httpClient will be closed automatically. No need of separate finally block.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "ebd19a1b168eb87cb9a2a317c4d28a4ccb67eb7e",
        "author": {
